Title: Series III Dudley Watch Co. 19 Jewel 12 Size Pocket Watch with Exhibition Back
Description: Series III Dudley Watch Co. 16-Size Man’s Pocket Watch with Exhibition Back U.S.; Dudley Watch Co.; Man’s; Serial# 6,188; CA1960’s CASE: The yellow gold-filled, 16-size, open face case has an exhibition back. DIAL: This silver metal dial displays Arabic numerals and cathedral hands. MOVT: This 19-jewel, stem-set movement with lever escapement is gilt with a bridge style layout and is signed. C 3 (The case is in very good condition) D 3-25 (The dial is in very good condition, partly rubbed) M 3 (The movement is in very good condition) R 8 (Rarity on a scale of #1 being very common to #10 being extremely rare) When you buy your first Dudley most collectors want an example of all three types. This is a very solid Series III!
